    %p Dear applicant,  
    
    %p We are delighted to welcome you as a Professional Networking Participant (PNP) to SUPERMARKET 2020!

    %p Please confirm your participation as soon as possible by logging in to your online application (www.supermarketartfair.com/user) and check the “Agreement of terms and regulations” box. We will send you an invoice for the participation fee by email in January. The participation fee for the PNP programme is SEK 2000 + VAT (SEK 2500 incl. VAT ≈ € 233 ≈ $ 256) Please make sure your invoice address, email address and VAT info is correct.

    %p Please inform us if you are waiting for funding approval and need more time to confirm your application.

    %p If you need a letter of invitation for funding applications, visa invitation, or have other questions, please contact us at info@supermarketartfair.com

    %p We are looking forward to hearing from you and meeting you soon in Stockholm!
    
    %p Kind Regards, 
    %p &nbsp;
    %p 
      The SUPERMARKET 2020 Selection Committee
      %br/
      Alice, Pontus, Andreas and Paulina
